posting_body: ['Resort-style living gets a new meaning at Village on Main Apartments – located on the Point Ruston waterfront in Tacoma.', 'Enjoy a truly modern urban village experience with countless dining, shopping, and recreation options right outside your doorstep.', 'Not to mention the coveted amenities and unequaled interiors available to residents right within the community.', '-50 onsite retail with unique eateries and shopping right at your doorstep', '-Air conditioning with programmable remote thermostat                                                                                        Featured amenity', '-Package locker with 24/7 access to packages', '-Private balcony or patio                                                                                        Featured amenity', '-Polished granite kitchen countertops', '-In-home washer and dryer                                                                                        Featured amenity', '-Worry-free 24-hour onsite maintenance', '-Expansive bay windows with 2-inch wood blinds', '-9-foot ceilings', '-Private parking garage with direct access elevators                                                                                         Featured amenity', '-Move-in with NO SECURITY DEPOSIT:', 'Only a small one-time payment', '-Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply)                                                                                    Photo                                                                                                                                 Featured amenity', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices Change Daily', 'Flexible Lease Terms']
